== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2019年5月20日，在《[[捍衛任務3：全面開戰|捍衛任務3：全面開戰]]》上映後，[[獅門娛樂|獅門娛樂]]宣布正在製作第四部《捍衛任務》電影，上映日期定於2021年5月27日<ref>{{Cite web|last=Alexander|first=Bryan|title='John Wick: Chapter 4' underway, but don't expect a 'happy ending' for Keanu Reeves|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2019/05/20/john-wick-chapter-4-keanu-reeves-fourth-movie-coming/3748121002/|access-date=2020-08-19|website=USA TODAY|archive-date=2020-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200608163821/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2019/05/20/john-wick-chapter-4-keanu-reeves-fourth-movie-coming/3748121002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年12月20日，據報導[[基努·李維|基努·李維]]已開始接受《捍衛任務4》和《[[駭客任務4|駭客任務4]]》的訓練<ref>{{Cite web|date=2019-12-20|title=Keanu Reeves is Training to Kill Everyone Again (in 'John Wick 4' and 'The Matrix 4')|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/keanu-reeves-training/|access-date=2020-08-19|website=/Film|archive-date=2020-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721160157/https://www.slashfilm.com/keanu-reeves-training/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年5月1日，受[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]影響，本片延期至2022年5月27日在美國上映，原上映日期由《[[死亡漩渦：奪魂鋸新遊戲|死亡漩渦：奪魂鋸新遊戲]]》接檔<ref name="NewDate" />。2020年8月初，獅門娛樂執行長{{le|喬恩·費瑟莫|Jon Feltheimer}}表示希望可以在2021年初以[[背靠背電影製作|背靠背]]形式同時拍攝《捍衛任務4》及其續集《[[捍衛任務5|捍衛任務5]]》<ref>{{Cite web|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|date=2020-08-06|title='John Wick 5' Greenlit by Lionsgate; Will Be Shot Back-to-Back with 'John Wick 4'|url=https://collider.com/john-wick-5-filming-dates-details-john-wick-4-keanu-reeves/|access-date=2020-08-19|website=Collider|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809072949/https://collider.com/john-wick-5-filming-dates-details-john-wick-4-keanu-reeves/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|date=2020-08-06|title=‘John Wick 5’ Confirmed By Lionsgate; Sequel Will Be Shot Back To Back With Fourth Installment|url=https://deadline.com/2020/08/john-wick-5-confirmed-by-lionsgate-sequel-will-be-shot-back-to-back-with-fourth-installment-1203006611/|access-date=2020-08-19|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819230331/https://deadline.com/2020/08/john-wick-5-confirmed-by-lionsgate-sequel-will-be-shot-back-to-back-with-fourth-installment-1203006611/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年1月，[[伊恩·麥克夏恩|伊恩·麥克夏恩]]表示拍攝將於2021年開始進行<ref>{{cite web|last=Gemmill|first=Allie|url=https://collider.com/john-wick-4-filming-start-date/|title='John Wick 4' Could Start Filming This Year, According to Ian McShane|publisher=[[Collider|Collider]]|date=2021-01-17|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522210441/https://collider.com/john-wick-4-filming-start-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年3月，據報導《捍衛任務4》和《捍衛任務5》將不再採用背靠背方式拍攝<ref name="Filming">{{cite web|last=Weintraub|first=Steve|url=https://collider.com/john-wick-4-filming-story-details/|title=Exclusive: ‘John Wick 4’ and ‘5’ Are Not Filming Back-to-Back; Plus Where and When ‘Wick 4’ Is Shooting|publisher=[[Collider|Collider]]|date=2021-03-23|accessdate=2021-04-11|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410002922/https://collider.com/john-wick-4-filming-story-details/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而《捍衛任務4》的劇本不再由系列創作人[[德瑞克·柯斯達|德瑞克·柯斯達]]撰寫，改由{{le|沙伊·哈頓|Shay Hatten}}和麥可·芬奇（{{lang|en|Michael Finch}}）共同編劇<ref>{{cite web|last=Davids|first=Brian|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/chad-stahelski-john-wick-4-his-matrix-4-involvement-1296473|title=Filmmaker Chad Stahelski on ''John Wick 4'' and His ''Matrix 4'' Involvement|date=2020-05-29|website=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2021-04-09|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502165139/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/chad-stahelski-john-wick-4-his-matrix-4-involvement-1296473|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Pearson|first=Ben|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/john-wick-4-and-5-writer/|title=''John Wick 4'' and ''John Wick 5'' Will Not Be Written by Franchise Architect Derek Kolstad; ''The Continental'' Announcements Coming Soon|date=2021-03-22|website=/Film|accessdate=2021-04-09|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324182022/https://www.slashfilm.com/john-wick-4-and-5-writer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

