ase Dates|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/lionsgate-hitmans-wifes-bodyguard-john-wick-chapter-4-1234595835/|accessdate=2020-05-01|website=[[Variety_(website)|Variety]]|archive-date=2020-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200501225824/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/lionsgate-hitmans-wifes-bodyguard-john-wick-chapter-4-1234595835/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

